# ===========================================================================
# AshDraftCore — standalone Game Feature Plugin repository .gitignore
#
# This repo IS the plugin. Drop it into a Lyra clone at:
#   <LyraProject>/Plugins/GameFeatures/AshDraftCore/
# then apply Docs/PROJECT_INTEGRATION.md.
#
# NOTE: Vendored art (Content/Data/Hero/ParagonSunWukong/) IS committed here
# as plain Git objects — it is intentionally NOT ignored. Git LFS is not used
# (largest file is under GitHub's 100 MB limit). See Docs/PROJECT_INTEGRATION.md.
# ===========================================================================

# --- Engine-generated / transient ---
Binaries/
Intermediate/
Saved/
DerivedDataCache/

# --- Generated IDE / solution files ---
*.sln
*.suo
*.user
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
*.sdf
.vs/
*.xcodeproj/
*.xcworkspace/

# --- Compiled binaries ---
*.dll
*.exe
*.lib
*.pdb
*.so
*.dylib
*.app

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*~
*.swp
*.stackdump
